<br>
I have noticed the 4 different kinds of pets including the chain rooter (which I don't like that much cuz if I wanted a chain rooter i'd just use the earth pet and have him deal a lot of damage at the same time.)  <br>
<br>
I've never seen the pet cast bonds of force though. <p><center><i><b>
